Package: owidR
Type: Package
Title: A Package for Importing Data from Our World in Data
Version: 1.4.0
Author: Piers York
Maintainer: Piers York <piersyork@gmail.com>
Description: owidR imports data from the Our World in Data website, offering easy to use functions for searching for datasets and importing them into R.
